    public class HistogramDataset
extends org.jfree.data.statistics.SimpleHistogramDataset
implements org.jfree.data.xy.IntervalXYDataset, org.jfree.data.general.DatasetChangeListener
    The dataset defines a histogram data set. A dataset contains multiple series each containing the entries to display.
